{"tid":2272702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［突發］國安處舉報熱線於11月5日正式啟用！","createTime":"2020-11-05T08:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T12:00:06.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"00f2a2e122ff6ab158e3803ac125ba682a59d20a","tid":2272702,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:21:54.000Z","msg":"【 國安處舉報熱線 】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xd5aEgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXd5aEgO.jpg&h=225a299f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了便利市民提供與國家安全相關的資料或舉報，香港警務處國家安全處已於今日(11月5號)正式啟用「國安處舉報熱線」。市民可以透過微信、電話短訊，或者專設電郵，多平台作出與國家安全相關的非緊急舉報。<br />\n<br />\n「國安處舉報熱線」只接收與國家安全相關的情報，包括資料、相片、錄音或錄像。電話熱線並不會接聽任何來電，亦不設回覆。另外，熱線並非用作一般報案，如需報案，請大家致電就近警署或999。警方不會透過此熱線索取你的個人資料。所有收集得到的資料，不會向第三方披露，並將會嚴格按照個人資料（私隱）條例處理。"},{"pid":"1eb96ba1c8fd4ade50f31114733dbac2060a94ec","tid":2272702,"uid":165749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"係咪拎黎舉報爛屍架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a1b57ca77a2da112398220009cdaf8f1ca8d61","tid":2272702,"uid":369011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"告發港獨之父689<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745eca80cb4ff6a2646b99bfc3c349928af7e1c4","tid":2272702,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:28:47.000Z","msg":"New Toy?"},{"pid":"77ff1d18b47b5cb2937fffa085e05f0a66e21d7b","tid":2272702,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"警察 ➡️ 國安<br />\n<br />\n警務署 ➡️ 國安公署"},{"pid":"29bc53638e416aab9c19ad7b2381935394ac383e","tid":2272702,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9ab8cfa5e77572342f7aa611736b2b7dfdc6cee","tid":2272702,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime